                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Finally, although most trajectories obtained during evaluation express promising and valuable results (Figure 5), they also present a significant degree of instability, which warrants additional research. This behavior is particularly evident in 5b where the model is trained using the function in Eq. 2. This model has had several transfers significantly faster than the ones in 5a and 5c as well as those obtained with SCP; nonetheless, the model has proved considerably slower in average."
